Name: Average time from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Request Payment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR' to 'Request Payment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Total time from 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' to 'Request Payment'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Minimum time from 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' to 'Request Payment'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Average time for 'Request Payment' to be processed after 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Total resolution time of 'Request Payment' in cases where 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' occurred
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Average waiting time to 'Request Payment' after 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Total time it takes 'Request Payment' to be done after 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Minimum time for 'Request Payment' to be processed in cases without 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'
Metric: the minimum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` != 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' and the last time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Request Payment'

Name: Average time it takes from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Request Payment' in cases leading to 'Payment Handled'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Total time for 'Request Payment' in variants where 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' precedes it directly
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Minimum time it takes from 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' to 'Request Payment' in cases where the declaration is resubmitted and approved
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' to 'Request Payment' in cases where the declaration is resubmitted and finally approved
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Total time for 'Request Payment' in cases with prior 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'Request Payment' in the process variant ending with 'Payment Handled' without prior rejections
Metric: the minimum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` != 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' and the last time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Request Payment' filtered by the function ma > 0 where ma is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'Payment Handled'
